Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:01:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有我們的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無形境界線什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無形境界線是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為十花小姐說得很對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想正是因為明白這一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為明白這一點  六花才會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算別人說「這就是現實  你必須接受」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有許多無法承受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一波未平一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來得及整理自己的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在逃避  也不打算忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以這種理所當然的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受這些所謂理所當然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大家都說這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說現實就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就真的沒有問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都是這樣活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:23.24,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,500)\pos(95,386)}第八集{\fs32}{\alpha&HFF}\Naaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}E   x   i   l   e\N{\fs0}兩個人的…  逃避之行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才坐計程車回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大概又去海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她回來前  大家都去海邊放煙花了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了解放暗黑龍的時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來  要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  富樫君和六花好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假來到海邊  兩人再悄悄出門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是去邂逅平行世界的戰士了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是修羅場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修羅場是強力的結界魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  還好趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要說的話  你打算去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方  管理局的勢力實在太大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界的力量太強了  只能撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太是從哪裡獲得了黑暗火焰的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那些東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始也就只是朋友之間說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都說一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們之間有一種違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是一種脫離於世界般的  奇妙的孤獨感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑暗意識喚醒了其他世界的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也有過這種感覺  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  是管理局的干擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視線對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  我們就締結了更高一級的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗火焰的懷抱中…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別玩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:06.12,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰が気付けただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:13.24,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}光の向こうで　濃くなる影に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:19.16,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}過去が遠くで叫んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:25.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}背中向ければ　耳を塞いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.43,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}辛くからって　弱いと決めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:37.72,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}泣かないからって　強いと思わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:44.00,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君が握る手　溫かさを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:50.02,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}信じてみてもいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:56.96,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やっと気付いた　ようやく見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:03.11,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}涙でぼやけた真実
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:09.31,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕は僕でいいと　頭を撫でながら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:15.78,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眠る君の橫顔が今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:22.64,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新しい気持ちを照らした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.54,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ありがとう　そばにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:35.28,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}芽吹いたよ　始まりの種が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:06.12,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是否有人會察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:13.24,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在光明的另一端  漸漸清晰的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:19.16,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}過去在遠方呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:25.10,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}轉過身去  充耳不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.43,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要因為痛苦  就否定我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:37.72,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然我不流淚  但不意味著堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:44.00,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你緊握的手  傳來的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:50.02,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是否可以依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:56.96,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於察覺  終於發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:03.11,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被淚水模糊的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:09.31,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你輕撫著我的頭  讓我勇敢做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:15.78,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此時此刻  你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:22.64,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照亮了我嶄新的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.54,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感謝你能陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:35.28,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新生的種子  已經發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說小鳥遊同學要回家  所以去送她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  裝純也要有個限度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和男生交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  幼稚園時和同班的隆君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之後因為爸爸工作的原因去了國外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學和初中都沒怎麼上過  一直是請家教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙難道就是傳說中真正的天然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守的身體就如同伊卡洛斯的翅膀一般被太陽灼傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難得的機會  我就幫你搓搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有個不錯的絲瓜瓤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心… 心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz13.72\fn方正報宋_GBK\pos(286,48)}收件箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\fn方正報宋_GBK\pos(648,72)\frz13.72}富樫勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz13.72\fn方正報宋_GBK\pos(527,173)}無題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正仿宋_GBK\pos(437,533)}先回去了。\N六花也跟我一起。\N請不用擔心。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得還真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  我進不了房門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼被修改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是忘記帶鑰匙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是管理局的襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要對我的家人動手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那麼不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樟葉和夢葉去林間夏令營了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽去上夜班了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點  這裡可能還被偽裝過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…  大家要明天才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就只有我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  廁所在哪邊來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯茗學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君也醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得天黑時的月亮好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想去散散步來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君也一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回答也太敷衍人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己有了女朋友就不管哥們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學的時候  我幫你創造搭訕機會的大恩你都忘光了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便打開我的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快收起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是對我邪王真眼也不能透露的終極裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先這樣綁上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能裝在這裡了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一甩手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要熱淚盈眶好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼向你致以無盡的敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過家裡也沒什麼像樣的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不出像十花小姐那樣的大手筆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其吃這個  我寧願空手打最終BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真堅定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要去便利店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要吃便利商店裡賣的食物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖料理人不准我吃那裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我必須吃她做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你應該謝謝她才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想吃這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在學校看勇太吃過  所以一直很好奇它的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先撕開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後分離表皮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉住兩邊這樣扯一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十花小姐要是看到了會生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  還有炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別有風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太的飯團是什麼味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗嘗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償給你這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色代表危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次果然不會上當了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那麼回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去沐浴一下月光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是晚上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人獨處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的「萬事俱備只欠告白」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊  你也太薄情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我開學時好心和你搭話的恩情都忘光了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請您等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小鳥遊同學怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛吃完飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙忘帶家裡的鑰匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  該不會也是兩人獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:16:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就覺得你們兩個很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到發展這麼迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在誤會什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種劇情根本不可能發生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是六花哦  中二病全開的六花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(477,284)}你的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(504,373)}好像要講很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(516,472)}我就先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(739,623)}枯茗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會不會  不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  那個滿腦子中二的六花根本就沒有戀愛的念頭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  這是雷霆戰錘之衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別甩了  會把衣服撐大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袖子挽起來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想像力還真豐富啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就睡這個房間吧  趕緊去刷牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勇太的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勇太的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  感覺好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那關燈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜正是邪王真眼狀態全滿的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼我的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了讓你睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺心神不寧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕它們已經來到這附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要加強戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心神不寧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心砰砰地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在給主題公園做廣告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爆發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  閉上眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一下  稍微一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  這樣真的好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等一下…  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對效力魔法碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才新締結的契約之印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別畫在這麼顯眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡最合適
